  "title": "Guide on creating a custom calendar widget",
  "body": "A calendar widget can be pretty important in certain use case. However there are many out there and adding one would have a direct impact on the library size. Also this requires to format data in a specific way.\r\n\r\nAs a first step we should provide a guide that explains how to integrate a calendar and format the data correctly so that it can be leverages using numeric filters. Maybe we should talk about the case when we want a range and a single date.\r\n\r\nIt should be possible to base the implementation on the connectors we currently have.",
